title: Did Jared Kushner-Owned Properties in Baltimore Violate Building Code Rules on Rodent Infestation?
subtitle: Some news reports saw a measure of irony in President Donald Trump's attacks on the city of Baltimore in July 2019.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: Properties owned by Jared Kushner in the Baltimore area have accrued multiple building code violations for rodent infestation.
